# .sivacorignore -- gitignore-style patterns for files to EXCLUDE from the
# redistributed replication package / TRO output. Matched files are still
# present during execution (so the code runs); they are simply not
# republished in the certified output.

# Confidential firm survey microdata (Data Use Agreement; not redistributable).
# Exclude everything in the folder, then re-include the .sivacorkeep placeholder
# via gitignore-style negation so the directory is retained in the output while
# the confidential data is withheld.
data/raw-confidential/*
!data/raw-confidential/.sivacorkeep

# Git directory-placeholder files: no meaning in the distributed package
.gitkeep
